headline: Extra Eyes: APS, Firefighters Team Up With New AI Smoke-Detection Cameras
summary: PHOENIX, March 25, 2025--Arizona Public Service's new artificial intelligence (AI) cameras are proactively searching 24/7 for early signs of wildfires in targeted areas.
